Vanessa Lee Evigan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vanessa_Lee_Evigan 0 Vanessa Lee Evigan (born March 18, 1981) is an American actress. She is the daughter of actor Greg Evigan and model and actress Pamela Serpe. She is also the sister of actress Briana Evigan and singer-songwriter Jason Evigan.
